71
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:25,000
not only alienated the Leng father and daughter,

72
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:27,040
but also broke through Leng Qingqiu's defenses,

73
00:04:27,319 --> 00:04:29,199
making her completely devoted to him.

74
00:04:29,439 --> 00:04:30,720
This man's scheming is so deep,

75
00:04:30,879 --> 00:04:32,000
it's absolutely outrageous.

76
00:04:32,399 --> 00:04:34,040
What exactly are you trying to do?

77
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:36,519
Are you trying to stop me from uniting Haicheng?

78
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,399
There are changes at the border now.

79
00:04:38,519 --> 00:04:39,720
Haicheng cannot fall into chaos.

80
00:04:40,439 --> 00:04:42,079
Keeping you alive

81
00:04:42,079 --> 00:04:43,600
will only lead to endless trouble.

82
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:45,439
I will kill this scoundrel right now.

83
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:48,680
Gu Zhantian will protect you all.

84
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:50,199
Stop bothering me.

85
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,480
Mom.

86
00:04:51,639 --> 00:04:53,079
I miss you so much.

87
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:56,199
When will you recover from your illness?

88
00:04:58,319 --> 00:04:59,399
So full of tricks.

89
00:05:01,279 --> 00:05:02,079
Young Master.

90
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:02,839
Why?

91
00:05:02,839 --> 00:05:04,000
Why do I feel

92
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,639
