183
00:08:32,639 --> 00:08:33,519
Thank you, Mr. Lu.

184
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:41,840
What's wrong?

185
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:42,919
The surgery was too exhausting.

186
00:08:42,919 --> 00:08:43,879
The surgery was too exhausting, huh?

187
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:44,240
Let's go.

188
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:45,120
I'll take you home.

189
00:08:45,639 --> 00:08:46,440
To your place.

190
00:08:47,039 --> 00:08:49,240
My dad hates it when I go into surgery.

191
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,039
No way.

192
00:08:51,399 --> 00:08:52,919
Didn't you say once Gu Zhantian leaves,

193
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:54,639
I could do whatever I want?

194
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:58,799
Someone's going back on their word, huh?

195
00:08:58,879 --> 00:09:00,799
I don't think Gu Zhantian has gone far.

196
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:01,919
Help, pervert!

197
00:09:05,519 --> 00:09:06,720
Shh, shh, shh!

198
00:09:26,879 --> 00:09:28,279
When are you finally leaving?

199
