213
00:10:16,919 --> 00:10:17,919
You're a girl.

214
00:10:17,919 --> 00:10:19,480
Mind your image, will you?

215
00:10:19,679 --> 00:10:21,240
What's wrong with being a girl?

216
00:10:22,279 --> 00:10:23,240
Brother Chengwen.

217
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:25,120
Do you want me

218
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:26,480
to train you a bit?

219
00:10:28,879 --> 00:10:30,080
Don't go too far.

220
00:10:30,279 --> 00:10:31,519
Do you hate me?

221
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:35,519
I don't exactly

222
00:10:35,519 --> 00:10:36,720
hate you.

223
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:39,000
You used to ignore me.

224
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:40,200
But recently, you suddenly

225
00:10:40,399 --> 00:10:42,039
started clinging to me.

226
00:10:42,039 --> 00:10:43,840
This is too big of a change.

227
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:45,120
You

228
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:49,639
don't like me clinging to you?

229
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:52,799
I don't like it.

230
00:10:53,039 --> 00:10:54,080
Not one bit.

231
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:55,080
Then have a drinking contest with me.

232
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:55,519
If you win,

233
00:10:55,519 --> 00:10:56,679
I'll never bother you again.

234
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:07,399
No.

235
00:11:14,879 --> 00:11:15,639
Help, pervert!

236
00:11:17,919 --> 00:11:18,720
Help, pervert!

237
00:11:20,279 --> 00:11:21,080
Help, pervert!
